</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>WhatsApp 資料從 Android 轉移 iOS    Apple 官方「Move to iOS」快將正式支援</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/06/14/move-to-ios-whatsapp/mobile-phone/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=move-to-ios-whatsapp</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Lawton]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Tue, 14 Jun 2022 13:00:41 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[Android App]]></category><category><![CDATA[手提電話]]></category><category><![CDATA[android]]></category><category><![CDATA[Apple]]></category><category><![CDATA[Move to iOS]]></category><category><![CDATA[WhatsApp]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1104637</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>Apple 今日正式發佈旗下的 Android 應用程式「Move to iOS」資料轉移工具即將正式支援 W [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Apple 今日正式發佈旗下的 Android 應用程式「<a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.apple.movetoios&amp;hl=zh_HK&amp;gl=US">Move to iOS</a>」資料轉移工具即將正式支援 WhatsApp。用戶從 Android 系統轉用 iPhone 時，可使用此應用程式，轉移 WhatsApp 以及相片、行事曆、聯絡人、SMS 訊息、Google 帳戶等資料到新買入的 iPhone。</p><h2>相關影片</h2><p><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_93062"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Z0hgTq-nNRE?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/285512458_1242228286181857_5019472512006727780_n-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="wp-image-1104653 size-large aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/285512458_1242228286181857_5019472512006727780_n-1-579x900.jpg" alt="" width="579" height="900" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/285512458_1242228286181857_5019472512006727780_n-1-579x900.jpg 579w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/285512458_1242228286181857_5019472512006727780_n-1-373x580.jpg 373w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/285512458_1242228286181857_5019472512006727780_n-1.jpg 643w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 579px" /></a></p><p>WhatsApp 官方早前公佈會有正式途徑跨平臺轉移資料，事實上坊間一直有工具從 Android 平臺轉移資料到 iPhone。而今次 Apple 就比 WhatsApp 官方更早一步推出資料轉移的正式版工具。</p><p>Apple 表示，通過「Move to iOS」轉移資料，將不會通過互聯網傳送，兩部手機將建立單對單的 Wi-Fi 連接以傳送資料，減少洩漏個人資料的情況出現。而在資料傳送過程中，資料都會進行加密，Apple 將不會知悉用戶傳送的內容。</p><p>在傳送資料時，「Move to iOS」會自動偵測 Android 手機中的 App 是否有提供 iOS 版本。如有的話，Move to iOS 就可為用戶轉移資料，甚至可指示 iPhone 安裝該等應用程式。例如用戶想轉移 WhatsApp 資料，在新購入 iPhone 後，就毋須先在 iPhone 安裝 WhatsApp，讓轉移工具為你管理。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/285127522_1503598596735946_334011835359868638_n-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="wp-image-1104652 size-large aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/285127522_1503598596735946_334011835359868638_n-1-578x900.jpg" alt="" width="578" height="900" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/285127522_1503598596735946_334011835359868638_n-1-578x900.jpg 578w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/285127522_1503598596735946_334011835359868638_n-1-372x580.jpg 372w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/285127522_1503598596735946_334011835359868638_n-1.jpg 642w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 578px" /></a></p><p>Apple 指資料只可從 Android 手機直接轉移到 iPhone，並不能把用戶備份在 Google Drive 的 WhatsApp 備份資料傳送到 iPhone。</p><p>同時用戶亦要留意，資料轉移後，在新機要使用相同的電話號碼（帳戶）登入 WhatsApp，才能取用轉移好的資料。</p><p>而一部份 WhatsApp 資料將不會通過「Move to iOS」直接轉移：</p><p>・涉及付款的訊息</p><p>・通話記錄</p><p>・用戶的顯示名稱</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-14-16.07.08.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1104660" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-14-16.07.08-694x458.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="458" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-14-16.07.08-694x458.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-14-16.07.08-1280x845.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-14-16.07.08-768x507.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-14-16.07.08.jpg 1327w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">「轉移至 iOS」Android 應用程式：<a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.apple.movetoios&amp;hl=zh_HK&amp;gl=US">Google Play 連結</a></p><p>資料來源：Apple</p><h2> 最新影片</h2><iframe style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;" id="_ytid_84661" width="590" height="332" data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/?enablejsapi=1&amp;list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl&amp;autoplay=0&amp;cc_load_policy=0&amp;cc_lang_pref=&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;loop=0&amp;modestbranding=1&amp;rel=0&amp;fs=1&amp;playsinline=1&amp;autohide=1&amp;theme=light&amp;color=white&amp;controls=0&amp;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen="" data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><div class="feedflare">
